[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0366","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0366.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0183","title":"Linux TFTP 实现目录遍历漏洞","description":"Linux系统的TFTP（Trivial File Transfer Protocol）实现中存在目录遍历漏洞，未限制文件访问路径。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过路径穿越技术访问TFTP根目录之外的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露，如密码文件等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0183"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到已修复此漏洞的TFTP服务器版本（如tftp-hpa），或配置chroot环境将TFTP服务限制在指定目录内，并禁用符号链接跟随以防止目录遍历攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T21:58:50.651362824+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0366.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0302","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0302.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0148","title":"SGI IRIX 6.4 CGI 处理程序远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 操作系统自带的 cgi-bin 处理器程序 handler 存在命令注入漏洞。该 CGI 程序未能正确过滤用户提供的 URL 参数，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，在受影响服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意系统命令。攻击复杂度低且无需身份验证，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0148"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5 或更高版本以修复 cgi-bin handler 的命令注入漏洞。如无法升级，在 /etc/cgi-bin/handler 配置中移除不必要的 CGI 映射，并在网络层面限制对 CGI 端口的访问。若环境允许，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/380","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19303"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19303"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0302.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0302.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0179","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0179.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0071","title":"Apache HTTP Server Cookie 处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.1.1 及更早版本的 cookie 处理函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未对输入长度进行充分校验。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 Cookie 数据触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致 httpd 进程崩溃或潜在远程代码执行。该漏洞影响所有运行受影响 Apache httpd 版本的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0071"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.2.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 cookie 处理函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。由于 1.2.0 版本也已停止维护，建议迁移至当前受支持的 Apache HTTP Server 版本（如 2.4.x），以确保获得持续的安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0071","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0071"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0179.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0081","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0024","title":"ISC BIND DNS 查询标识符可预测导致缓存投毒漏洞","description":"BIND DNS 服务器存在 DNS 缓存投毒漏洞，由于使用可预测的查询 ID 作为事务标识符，远程攻击者可通过向目标 DNS 服务器发送伪造的 DNS 响应报文，在无需认证的情况下实施缓存投毒攻击，将合法域名解析指向恶意 IP 地址，导致用户被重定向至恶意网站或遭受中间人攻击。该漏洞影响早期 BIND 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0024"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.577","remediation":"升级 BIND 至 4.9.7 或 8.2 及以上版本，该版本引入了随机化 DNS 查询 ID 机制，防止攻击者预测 ID 实施缓存投毒。若无法升级，可在 named.conf 中限制递归查询仅对受信任内部网段开放（allow-recursion），并在边界防火墙上阻断 UDP 53 端口的非授权外部访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0024"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0152","title":"Data General DG/UX finger 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"DG/UX 系统的 finger 服务程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 finger 服务发送包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）的特制请求，利用服务程序对用户输入过滤不严的缺陷，在目标系统上以 finger 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 DG/UX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击复杂度低，利用方式简单，影响较为广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0152"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.707","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（/etc/inetd.conf 中注释 finger 行并重启 inetd），或在防火墙层面阻止外部对 finger 端口（79/tcp）的访问。由于 DG/UX 已停止技术支持且无官方补丁，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0152"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0829","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0566","title":"IBM AIX syslog 日志填充拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统中的 syslog 组件存在日志写入权限缺陷，攻击者可从任意位置向 syslog 文件写入大量日志条目，导致磁盘空间被占满从而引发拒绝服务。同时，恶意日志会淹没正常审计记录，掩盖攻击者的操作痕迹，增加安全检测与溯源难度。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0566"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.053","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，安装 APAR IX87386 补丁。同时配置 syslogd 限制远程写入（修改 /etc/syslog.conf 禁用非必要远程日志接收），在 /etc/hosts.allow 中限制 syslog 端口（UDP 514）的访问来源，并启用日志轮转（logrotate）防止单一日志文件过大导致磁盘写满。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0566.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8aeb4aa9-e098-4c64-a9a7-a80928b5b3b8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0781","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0781.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0524","title":"Linux Kernel ICMP 时间戳和网络掩码信息泄露漏洞","description":"ICMP（互联网控制报文协议）地址掩码和时间戳响应可被任意主机触发，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统发送ICMP地址掩码请求或时间戳请求报文，从而获取目标网络的子网掩码、路由信息及系统时间等敏感数据。该漏洞广泛影响早期Linux内核版本及大量Unix类系统，攻击者可利用收集到的网络拓扑信息进行后续精准渗透攻击，属于信息泄露类漏洞，CVSS评分4.0，危害等级中危。通过操作系统层面禁用ICMP地址掩码和时间戳响应即可有效缓解。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0524"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.703","remediation":"在 `/etc/sysctl.conf` 中设置 `net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1` 并执行 `sysctl -p` 生效。使用 iptables 屏蔽入站 ICMP 时间戳请求 (`iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type 13 -j DROP`) 和地址掩码请求 (`iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type 17 -j DROP`)。如用 firewalld，执行 `firewall-cmd --permanent --direct --add-rule ipv4 filter INPUT 0 -p icmp --icmp-type timestamp-request -j DROP`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://descriptions.securescout.com/tc/11010","http://descriptions.securescout.com/tc/11011","http://kb.juniper.net/InfoCenter/index?page=content&id=JSA10705","http://kb.vmware.com/selfservice/microsites/search.do?cmd=displayKC&externalId=1434","http://www.osvdb.org/95","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/306","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/322","https://kc.mcafee.com/corporate/index?page=content&id=SB10053","https://support.f5.com/csp/article/K15277","https://github.com/noraj/ChronoLeak","https://github.com/threatlabindonesia/CVE-1999-0524-ICMP-Timestamp-and-Address-Mask-Request-Exploit","https://github.com/b1tsec/CVE-1999-0524","https://github.com/Ransc0rp1on/ICMP-Timestamp-POC"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0781.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0423","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0238","title":"PHP PHP/fi 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 2.0 的 php.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用路径遍历技术读取服务器上的任意文件，包括敏感配置文件、密码文件等。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 2.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，危害较大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0238"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.650","remediation":"立即移除或禁用 PHP/fi 2.0 中的 php.cgi 脚本，升级至 PHP 3.0 或更高版本（PHP 3.0 起已重写架构并修复此目录遍历问题）。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中限制 php.cgi 仅访问指定目录，或通过 .htaccess / httpd.conf 禁止直接访问该脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0238","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0238","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0238.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj/GHSA-r5ff-p26w-7pfj.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0238.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0238.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2250/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0423.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0423.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0498","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0301","title":"SunOS/Solaris ps 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SunOS 和 Solaris 系统中的 ps 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 ps 命令传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限，实现完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 SunOS 5.3/5.4/5.5/5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等多个版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0301"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级到不受影响的 SunOS/Solaris 版本，或安装 Sun 安全公告 149 号提供的补丁程序。限制本地用户对 ps 命令的访问权限可缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:06:30.705882439+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/149"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0432","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0432.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0247","title":"INN nnrpd 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"INN (InterNetNews) 新闻服务器中的 nnrpd 程序存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞，版本 1.6 及之前版本受影响。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的新闻组请求，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在服务器上以 nnrpd 进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 INN 新闻服务器系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至 INN 1.6 以上版本修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0247"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.740","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.0 或更高版本，该漏洞在 INN 1.7 及后续版本中已被修复。如无法升级，可在 innd 配置中限制 nnrpd 服务的远程访问来源 IP，或禁用 nnrpd 的远程连接功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/17_inn_avd.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1443","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0247","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/inn.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0432.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0268","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0268.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0122","title":"IBM AIX lchangelv 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2 系统中的 /usr/sbin/lchangelv 工具存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以 root 权限执行任意代码。攻击者需要通过本地账户登录系统，向 lchangelv 程序提交特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖返回地址或函数指针劫持进程控制流。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 4.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，攻击前提是拥有本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0122"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.147","remediation":"IBM AIX 4.2 用户应立即升级至 AIX 4.3.3 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复；或安装对应 APAR 补丁包。临时缓解措施：以 root 权限执行 `chmod 500 /usr/sbin/lchangelv` 移除 setuid 位，限制普通用户执行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0122","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19309","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0122","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0122.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ccc7-4g5p-rggh/GHSA-ccc7-4g5p-rggh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--772eac60-d912-4492-9f00-76b00cf63353.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0268.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0092","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0092.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0030","title":"SGI IRIX xlock 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 系统及其他类 Unix 操作系统（包括 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、HP-UX、IBM AIX、Solaris）中 xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 xlock 发送特制输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响广泛的多款 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0030"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.497","remediation":"SGI IRIX 系统应立即升级 xlock 程序至厂商已修复版本（如 IRIX 6.4 对应安全补丁），其他受影响系统（BSD/OS 2.1、Debian 1.3、HP-UX 10.34、IBM AIX 4.2、Solaris 2.5.1 等）应从各自厂商获取 xlock 安全更新。若无法立即打补丁，作为临时缓解措施可移除 xlock 的 setuid root 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xlock），限制本地用户以提权方式运行 xlock 程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0030"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0092.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0091","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0091.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0028","title":"SGI IRIX login/scheme 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 系统的 login/scheme 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过向存在缺陷的命令提交超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞影响多个 SGI IRIX 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0028"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.163","remediation":"SGI IRIX 5.3/6.2/6.3/6.4/6.5 均受影响，应立即安装 SGI 对应版本的安全补丁（如 IRIX 6.5 安装 Patch 3180 或更新版本）。若无法立即打补丁，可执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/scheme` 移除 scheme 命令的 setuid 位，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0028"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0091.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0089","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0089.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0029","title":"SGI IRIX ordist 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 5.3 及 6.2 系统中的 ordist 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可向 ordist 命令提交特制请求触发缓冲区越界读取，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 5.3 和 6.2 版本，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地系统访问权限，属于本地权限提升漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0029"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.303","remediation":"安装 SGI 于 1997 年发布的 ordist 安全补丁（SGI Security Advisory 19970701），或升级到 IRIX 6.3 及以上版本。如无法升级，建议移除 ordist 的 setuid root 权限：chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ordist，并限制仅授信用户可本地登录系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0029","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19317","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0029.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0029","https://github.com